Description: add fullscreen toggle with F key and fix letterbox clearing
 Press F to toggle between windowed and fullscreen (desktop resolution, no
 mode change). SDL_WINDOWEVENT_SIZE_CHANGED replaces SDL_WINDOWEVENT_RESIZED
 so that programmatic fullscreen transitions update the viewport correctly.
 The render loop now clears the full window to black before restricting to
 the letterboxed viewport, so pillar/letterbox bars are always filled.
